data.text:
'Monster is gone': B'desh interim chief on Hasina's ouster, hails 'student-led revolution'

timesofindia.com / Aug 12, 2024, 20:38 (IST)

Mohammed Yunus, Nobel laureate and interim government chief of Bangladesh, praised a student-led revolution that led to the collapse of government machinery. The protests, addressing preferential quotas in government jobs, resulted in Sheikh Hasina fleeing to India. Yunus acknowledged the challenges faced by the interim government following the violent clashes between authorities and students, which caused significant turmoil.

Pak army arrests former ISI chief, initiates court martial proceedings

timesofindia.com / Aug 12, 2024, 19:31 (IST)

Former ISI chief Faiz Hameed was arrested by the Pakistan military due to a housing scheme scandal, marking the first court martial against an intelligence head in the nation's history. The Supreme Court had pressed for this after serious allegations from Top City regarding Hameed's misuse of power. An inquiry committee investigated, leading to Hameed's capture.

Why Sebi chief should appear before a multi-party panel of MPs

Aug 11, 2024, 21:22 (IST)

Regulators need autonomy from executive & accountability to public. That’s why the best forum for Sebi chief, who’s issued a statement, to explain herself is a multi-party committee of MPs

Kolkata doc murder case: Accused in custody, then why a demand for CBI probe?

timesofindia.com / Aug 12, 2024, 20:07 (IST)

West Bengal CM Mamata Banerjee warned police to resolve the Kolkata doctor rape-murder case by Sunday or transfer it to the CBI. The victim's family alleged a cover-up. The accused, a civic volunteer with police ties, was arrested, prompting nation-wide doctor protests. The case spurred demands for a CBI investigation and raised concerns about hospital security lapses.

Trump meltdown over crowd size at Kamala's rallies raises fears of mental decline

tnn / Aug 12, 2024, 19:58 (IST)

Concerns about Donald Trump's mental state escalated after he accused Kamala Harris of using AI to create fake crowd photos at her rallies. Trump demanded Harris' disqualification, calling it election interference. Republican and independent attendees refuted his claims by sharing real crowd footage. This incident has raised fears of Trump contesting future defeats similarly.

Why India’s first undersea train tunnel will be an engineering marvel

timesofindia.com / Aug 03, 2024, 22:05 (IST)

By 2028 when India’s first bullet train runs from Ahmedabad to Mumbai, it will pass under the ecologically sensitive Thane Creek. Here’s the lowdown on how NHSRCL is tackling complex environmental and geological challenges to build a 7-km underwater tunnel

Did Neeraj Chopra wear Rs 52 lakh-plus watch at Olympics final

timesofindia.com / Aug 12, 2024, 16:15 (IST)

Neeraj Chopra, the Olympic silver medalist javelin thrower, wore an Omega Seamaster Aqua Terra Ultralight watch worth over Rs 52 lakh during the 2024 Paris Olympics finals. Neeraj, sponsored by Omega, threw 89.45m to win silver against Pakistan's Arshad Nadeem, who secured gold with a 92.97m throw. The competition included top javelin throwers globally.

India awaits verdict on Vinesh's appeal against disqualification

timesofindia.com / Aug 12, 2024, 20:30 (IST)

The sports community in India anxiously awaited the Court of Arbitration for Sport's (CAS) decision on wrestler Vinesh Phogat's appeal against her disqualification from the Paris Olympics gold medal match in the women's 50kg freestyle event.Vinesh had secured her place in the final with impressive victories, including a win over Japan's renowned wrestler Yui Susaki. However, during the mandatory morning weigh-in, she was found to be 100gm over the allowed limit, resulting in her disqualification.

Happy Independence Day 2024: Top 50 wishes, messages and quotes

etimes.in / Aug 12, 2024, 21:00 (IST)

Independence Day in India, celebrated on August 15th, marks the significant moment in 1947 when India gained freedom from British rule. This special occasion honors the immense sacrifices made by countless individuals who fought for the nation’s independence. The day is a tribute to their bravery and dedication. To make this occasion even more meaningful and memorable here is a specially curated collection of the top 50 wishes, messages, and inspirational quotes to share with your loved ones.​
